    <h2>Time Selection</h2>
    <p>Did you notice the <strong>time slider</strong> at the bottom of the page? We already selected September 29th, 2011 for you.</p>
    <p>Try stretching the time interval at its ends or draw a new one and watch the satellite images adjusting. Only those acquired within the selected interval are displayed.</p>
    <p>Note that only the latest 100 satellite images are shown per tile. Thus when selecting a big time interval you might not see all images available.</p>
    <p>By the way, try the scroll wheel to uncover additional functionality.</p>
</section>
